TUTORIAL TIME!!
(Every character has some actions in the Skills section,
they depend on the type of player he/she is.)
("Inspect" is used to check the surroundings and look
for clues/traps/hidden paths. You will need to be next
to the thing you want to inspect in order to interact
with it this way.)
("Attack front" is for warriors (melee characters), and
it will allow you to hit whatever you have in front,
making it usefull to break things.)
("Dispell Illusion" is used to reveal hidden paths
hidden by magic, you need to be near the area of the
path to discover it with this action.)
("Desintegrate" is used to break walls, but most of the
inner tomb is protected with a great spell that
nullifies it, so don't make it your first option.)
(That's all the help you are going to get, so good
luck!)
P.S. Try not to die a lot :D
